(888, 'Pascal Vice-champion d\'Europe !!', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Nouvelle m&eacute;daille internationale pour Pascal Martinot-Lagarde qui a r&eacute;ussi &agrave; d&eacute;crocher la 2e place du 60m haies des championnats d&#39;Europe de Prague!</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"/news.php?url=1&amp;id=726\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Tenant du titre</span></a>, PML a conclu sa course en 7&quot;52 &agrave; 1 petit centi&egrave;me du&nbsp;<span style=\" color:#000000;\">podium&nbsp;</span>!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>F&eacute;licitations !!</strong></p>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-video\" data-lang=\"fr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">\r\n		Pascal Martinot-Lagarde termine 2e du 60m haies pour un centi&egrave;me ! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Belgrade2017?src=hash\">#Belgrade2017</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Athl%C3%A9tisme?src=hash\">#Athl&eacute;tisme</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/e9XvXrufTN\">pic.twitter.com/e9XvXrufTN</a></p>\r\n	&mdash; francetv sport (@francetvsport) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/francetvsport/status/837746118570225666\">3 mars 2017</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\r\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-video\" data-lang=\"fr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">\r\n		&Agrave; un centi&egrave;me de l&#39;or, Pascal Martinot-Lagarde a refait la course avec nos envoy&eacute;s sp&eacute;ciaux <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Belgrade2017?src=hash\">#Belgrade2017</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/TLS?src=hash\">#TLS</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/Xanfa4A6Xh\">pic.twitter.com/Xanfa4A6Xh</a></p>\r\n	&mdash; francetv sport (@francetvsport) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/francetvsport/status/838110216222822400\">4 mars 2017</a></blockquote>\r\n<script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>', '2017-03-04 22:09:25', 1, 'Competitions', NULL, 3, 'uploads/pacal-matinot-lagarde-2018.jpg', 'Pascal Martinot 2e a Prague sur 60m haies'),
